name: Free Audio 4 Artists!
description:
Day 32 multiple editions. Music Day 2. Today I am bringing you music again! Yes music is art too! For 1 week straight I will be releasing audio art.
These sounds just like my other creations are made by me and are free to you to use in anyway you would like. Commercial rights are granted to the owner of this NFT. Please use this sound to accompany and compliment a visual component created by you. Credits are cool too
